54
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:21,650
- Hey, Oppa.
- Yeah?

55
00:08:21,650 --> 00:08:23,940
Press Director Soh wants to grab a meal together.

56
00:08:23,940 --> 00:08:26,630
Eating with Director Soh is your business.

57
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:27,850
Thanks, Seung Hwa.

58
00:08:27,850 --> 00:08:30,930
Oppa, how can you say that?

59
00:08:30,930 --> 00:08:35,090
Do you know how much I compliment you with Director Soh?

60
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,900
Thanks.

61
00:08:37,900 --> 00:08:40,350
But can you stop calling me "Oppa"?

62
00:08:40,350 --> 00:08:42,310
Why? You're an oppa.

63
00:08:42,310 --> 00:08:43,930
You're older than me.

64
00:08:43,930 --> 00:08:46,370
Yeah, I know, but...

65
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:58,550
Hyung!

66
