68
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:05,470
"Don't call me that."

69
00:09:05,470 --> 00:09:09,230
That's what I said, but she keeps doing it.

70
00:09:09,230 --> 00:09:11,210
Then, make a serious face.

71
00:09:11,210 --> 00:09:14,810
Make a serious face? Great idea.

72
00:09:14,810 --> 00:09:17,190
- Is that it?
- No.

73
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:20,750
Has Ju Eun Ho reached out?

74
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:24,100
No. She hasn't.

75
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:47,320
Oh, yes. I was about to mention it.

76
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:50,820
Yes, yes. Get home safe.

77
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:56,870
Hey. They say you're back on "Current News at Ten."

78
00:09:56,870 --> 00:10:01,160
Is this a joke? I already quit that program.

79
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:05,510
Exactly. I also thought that, so I asked several times.

80
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:07,910
"Really? Are you sure?

81
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:11,600
Are you sure you're talking about Jung Hyun Oh?

82
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,900
Not someone with the same name?

83
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:20,600
But why are you asking for Jung Hyun Oh, who didn't make the 9 o'clock news?

84
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:25,470
You know? He lost his seat to Jeon Jae Yong,

85
00:10:25,470 --> 00:10:29,030
and he's been an outcast with nowhere to go.

86
00:10:29,030 --> 00:10:33,560
Every other month, he waters the cactus on our office windowsill.

87
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,450
His nickname these days...

88
00:10:35,450 --> 00:10:37,970
is the spray bottle of the announcer world.

89
00:10:37,970 --> 00:10:39,860
You know, spray bottles?

90
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:43,150
Are you sure you want that Announcer Jung Hyun Oh back?"

91
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:44,960
And they said yes.

92
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:52,100
So, just say, "Aigoo, thank you," and get back in there next month.

93
00:10:56,050 --> 00:10:59,860
Don't you think it'll be kind of funny?

94
00:11:01,310 --> 00:11:02,980
Funny how?

95
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:07,830
Do you want me to tell you again why none of this is funny?

96
00:11:07,830 --> 00:11:12,390
Where should I start? Explaining why you've been an outcast?

97
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:14,560
Never mind. Got it.

98
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:16,500
Thank you, Team Leader.

99
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:21,230
I'll get right in there. Good?

100
00:11:21,230 --> 00:11:23,050
Hey, Hyun Oh.

101
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:26,960
Well, you know...

102
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:29,980
have you heard from Eun Ho?

103
00:11:32,810 --> 00:11:33,980
No.

104
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:35,960
I mean...

105
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:39,360
