106
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:44,350
And she ran off after she heard you're getting married. Right?

107
00:11:44,350 --> 00:11:46,010
Hey. Team Leader.

108
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:50,490
Hey. I'm just talking about the timing.

109
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:53,500
- But are you seriously getting married-
- No, I'm not.

110
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:55,190
I'm not. Never.

111
00:11:55,190 --> 00:11:58,050
Hey. Good call.

112
00:11:58,050 --> 00:12:01,830
Wow. I wish Eun Ho would find out about that.

113
00:12:01,830 --> 00:12:04,590
But where is she? Doing what?

114
00:12:04,590 --> 00:12:08,330
I heard she used all the vacation days that she piled up.

115
00:12:08,330 --> 00:12:10,900
- She probably went on a trip.
- Exactly.

116
00:12:10,900 --> 00:12:14,200
Where did she go that I haven't heard from her at all?

117
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:16,660
It's been a month.

118
00:12:16,660 --> 00:12:20,400
When she was in the office, it was so noisy.

119
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:22,150
But...

120
00:12:23,410 --> 00:12:26,200
