00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:56,450
Why not?

267
00:22:57,330 --> 00:22:59,430
Give it to me. I'll do it.

268
00:22:59,430 --> 00:23:04,610
I heard some people can open a bottle with paper.

269
00:23:05,490 --> 00:23:07,400
I think I can do that.

270
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:09,830
Sunbae, I think the opener is the problem.

271
00:23:09,830 --> 00:23:12,530
No, no. That's...

272
00:23:12,530 --> 00:23:14,700
Is it that difficult?

273
00:23:14,700 --> 00:23:16,150
Aigoo.

274
00:23:19,380 --> 00:23:21,120
Come in.

275
00:23:21,120 --> 00:23:22,800
Ju Yeon!

276
00:23:27,760 --> 00:23:29,920
- Department Head.
- Yes.

277
00:23:29,920 --> 00:23:32,630
I have a question.

278
00:23:32,630 --> 00:23:34,580
Go ahead!

279
00:23:35,390 --> 00:23:42,020
What does it mean if an announcer is taken off all of their programs at once?

280
00:23:42,990 --> 00:23:45,480
- That's...
- I know.

281
00:23:46,270 --> 00:23:48,880
That means she quit.

282
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:50,540
Aigoo, Hye Yeon.

283
00:23:50,540 --> 00:23:52,800
What? It's true.

284
00:23:52,800 --> 00:23:54,370
Am I wrong?

285
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:57,700
I think you're right, Hye Yeon.

286
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:59,490
Why do you ask, Ju Yeon?

287
00:24:00,260 --> 00:24:02,120
But Department Head,

288
00:24:02,120 --> 00:24:06,610
if they quit, their job wouldn't show up on their profile.

289
00:24:07,430 --> 00:24:09,800
Is that so?

290
00:24:09,800 --> 00:24:12,950
I know about that, too. That means she's taking a sabbatical.

291
00:24:12,950 --> 00:24:15,510
Hye Yeon, we don't have sabbaticals here.

292
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:18,150
No, but PPS does.

293
00:24:18,150 --> 00:24:20,760
It's very appealing to me.

294
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:24,050
Sunbae, that means she's taking a leave.

295
00:24:24,050 --> 00:24:26,510
A very long one.

296
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:29,290
But why? Do you need a break, too?

297
00:24:29,290 --> 00:24:31,720
If so, can you let me know? I want a break, too.

298
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:34,530
No. I don't want a break.

299
00:24:38,230 --> 00:24:40,190
- Thank you, Department Head.
- Sure.

300
00:24:40,190 --> 00:24:42,300
Huh? Why are you thanking him?

301
00:24:42,300 --> 00:24:45,150
I answered everything. You should thank me.

302
00:24:47,450 --> 00:24:49,690
So, in that spirit...

303
00:24:49,690 --> 00:24:52,570
- By the way, Department Head.
- Oh, what else?

304
00:24:54,100 --> 00:24:57,780
Do you know Announcer Jung Hyun Oh from PPS?

305
00:24:57,780 --> 00:24:59,880
Jung Hyun Oh?

306
00:25:57,300 --> 00:25:59,710
[Jung Hyun Oh profile]

307
00:25:59,710 --> 00:26:02,780
[Jung Hyun Oh]

308
00:26:34,140 --> 00:26:38,690
[Issue-In]

309
00:26:44,260 --> 00:26:46,250
Hello.

310
00:26:46,250 --> 00:26:48,280
I heard you came to see me.

311
00:26:49,910 --> 00:26:54,050
Hello. I'm Kang Ju Yeon from Media N Seoul.

312
00:26:54,050 --> 00:26:57,800
I'm Jung Hyun Oh. I think we've met once before.

313
00:27:00,780 --> 00:27:02,240
Yes.

314
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:10,560
What can I do for you?

315
00:27:12,280 --> 00:27:15,440
I'm here because I have some questions.

316
00:27:16,970 --> 00:27:18,910
Sure, go ahead.

317
00:27:26,350 --> 00:27:28,370
Where is...

318
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:31,590
Announcer Ju Eun Ho right now?

319
00:27:36,250 --> 00:27:38,750
I'd like to know first

320
00:27:39,650 --> 00:27:42,610
what your relationship is with Ju Eun Ho,

321
00:27:42,610 --> 00:27:45,450
and you'll have to explain to me

322
00:27:45,450 --> 00:27:48,170
why you're asking me that.

323
00:27:50,450 --> 00:27:52,920
Then, can I ask you, too?

324
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:57,300
Sunbaenim, what is your relationship to Ju Eun Ho?

325
00:27:59,060 --> 00:28:00,890
We're colleagues.

326
00:28:04,670 --> 00:28:06,290
Seriously...

327
00:28:08,010 --> 00:28:10,620
Why are you saying "Seriously"?

328
00:28:13,560 --> 00:28:17,220
Because I've seen you and Ju Eun Ho

329
00:28:17,220 --> 00:28:19,930
be loving with one another.

330
00:28:22,730 --> 00:28:25,700
Who are you to ask me such questions?

331
00:28:25,700 --> 00:28:28,840
As I've said before, I'm from Media N Seoul-

332
00:28:28,840 --> 00:28:30,120
No.

333
00:28:30,120 --> 00:28:33,530
I'm asking who you are to Ju Eun Ho.

334
00:28:36,660 --> 00:28:39,940
I'm in a relationship with Ju Hye Ri,

335
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:43,700
Ju Eun Ho's other personality.

336
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:54,500
Her other personality? What are you talking about?

337
00:28:54,520 --> 00:28:59,040
Ju Eun Ho said she has Dissociative Identity Disorder.

338
00:29:08,660 --> 00:29:11,420
I only found out recently.

339
00:29:15,600 --> 00:29:19,800
- Then how did you-
- Ju Eun Ho told me herself.

340
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:22,050
She told you directly?

341
00:29:25,870 --> 00:29:28,210
Then, you and Eun Ho...

342
00:29:28,210 --> 00:29:30,050
What did you say? A relationship?

343
00:29:30,050 --> 00:29:33,140
I'm in a relationship with Ju Hye Ri,

344
00:29:33,140 --> 00:29:35,950
her other personality.

345
00:29:38,980 --> 00:29:40,390
So...

346
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:43,700
Eun Ho has multiple personalities,

347
00:29:43,700 --> 00:29:46,200
and her other personality is Ju Hye Ri.

348
00:29:47,010 --> 00:29:48,890
But Ju Hye Ri...

349
00:29:48,900 --> 00:29:51,780
- Isn't that her younger sister's name?
- Yes.

350
00:29:52,660 --> 00:29:55,800
That's what Ju Eun Ho said, too.

351
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:58,590
That her other personality is her younger sister.

352
00:29:59,850 --> 00:30:02,030
Oh, so...

353
00:30:03,020 --> 00:30:05,530
You were dating Eun Ho's sister?

354
00:30:05,530 --> 00:30:10,020
Yes. I'm dating her younger sister.

355
00:30:10,970 --> 00:30:13,100
But you're saying that younger sister...

356
00:30:14,010 --> 00:30:15,960
is Eun Ho.

357
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:18,510
Then, you're saying you were dating Eun Ho. No?

358
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:20,340
That's true, but...

359
00:30:21,330 --> 00:30:24,660
the person I met was 28 years old

360
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:27,260
and worked in a parking lot.

361
00:30:27,260 --> 00:30:29,300
Her name is Hye Ri.

362
00:30:31,190 --> 00:30:35,960
Sunbaenim, did you not know about this at all?

363
00:30:38,030 --> 00:30:40,530
I-I'm really not Ju Eun Ho...

364
00:30:40,530 --> 00:30:43,270
What are you saying, Ju Eun Ho? Stop it!

365
00:30:43,270 --> 00:30:45,610
I said I'm not Ju Eun Ho!

366
00:30:45,610 --> 00:30:47,240
Hey, Ju Eun Ho!

367
00:30:54,800 --> 00:30:57,740
We had feelings for each other.

368
00:31:04,370 --> 00:31:05,900
Fine.

369
00:31:07,170 --> 00:31:10,760
Even if she has multiple personalities, it's still Eun Ho.

370
00:31:11,740 --> 00:31:13,960
Eun Ho had feelings for someone else?

371
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:16,140
What's odd about that?

372
00:31:17,020 --> 00:31:18,750
Because...

373
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:21,430
that...

374
00:31:22,540 --> 00:31:25,630
- Because Eun Ho-
- She likes you?

375
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:32,760
I have feelings for her.

376
00:31:34,660 --> 00:31:36,520
Do you mean...

377
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:39,580
you like Eun Ho, or Ju Hye Ri?

378
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:41,780
To be precise,

379
00:31:42,730 --> 00:31:44,930
I like Ju Hye Ri, who is inside Ju Eun Ho.

380
00:31:44,930 --> 00:31:46,450
So, that's Eun Ho.

381
00:31:46,450 --> 00:31:49,020
I would prefer that, too, Sunbaenim.

382
00:31:51,030 --> 00:31:54,550
I wish the person I met was Eun Ho.

383
00:31:55,320 --> 00:31:56,990
Because...

384
00:31:57,800 --> 00:31:59,740
no matter how long I wait,

385
00:32:00,620 --> 00:32:03,260
Hye Ri won't show up.

386
00:32:04,410 --> 00:32:09,570
So, I looked for Eun Ho, and she had disappeared.

387
00:32:09,570 --> 00:32:12,310
That's why I came here.

388
00:32:13,310 --> 00:32:16,020
I thought maybe you knew...

389
00:32:16,020 --> 00:32:18,550
where Ju Eun Ho was.

390
00:32:18,550 --> 00:32:21,780
Where she is and what she's doing.

391
00:32:22,680 --> 00:32:24,940
Do you happen to know?

392
00:32:27,290 --> 00:32:30,600
I want to see Ju Eun Ho.

393
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:34,500
I want her to be Hye Ri, but if not,

394
00:32:36,730 --> 00:32:39,020
I'd at least like to see Eun Ho

395
00:32:40,090 --> 00:32:43,010
and I have so much to tell her.

396
00:32:52,010 --> 00:32:55,400
Eun Ho took a leave of absence a month ago

397
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:57,480
and hasn't been back since.

398
00:32:59,410 --> 00:33:02,470
I can't reach her, either.

399
00:33:06,760 --> 00:33:08,540
I see.

400
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:13,330
Did Eun Ho...

401
00:33:14,590 --> 00:33:16,720
say she liked you?

402
00:33:20,780 --> 00:33:23,480
As I've said, Sunbaenim,

403
00:33:24,490 --> 00:33:28,560
Eun Ho never told me she liked me.

404
00:33:28,560 --> 00:33:30,630
Hye Ri, who is inside Eun Ho,

405
00:33:31,750 --> 00:33:35,450
and I shared feelings for each other.

406
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:40,060
So, are you broken up?

407
00:33:42,340 --> 00:33:43,720
No.

408
00:33:45,850 --> 00:33:47,860
Hye Ri just disappeared.

409
00:33:47,860 --> 00:33:49,820
So, if she comes back,

410
00:33:51,030 --> 00:33:53,310
will you date her again?

411
00:33:57,610 --> 00:33:59,150
Yes.

412
00:34:06,350 --> 00:34:08,870
Is that surprising to you, Sunbaenim?

413
00:34:11,300 --> 00:34:12,770
No.

414
00:34:15,070 --> 00:34:17,680
I'm surprised by too many things.

415
00:34:17,680 --> 00:34:19,950
I can't just pick one.

416
00:34:20,910 --> 00:34:22,520
But more than that...

417
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:27,020
the fact that you and Eun Ho were together, I just-

418
00:34:27,020 --> 00:34:31,220
Dissociative Identity Disorder. It's a disorder per its name.

419
00:34:31,220 --> 00:34:33,160
An illness.

420
00:34:34,880 --> 00:34:37,270
That means...

421
00:34:37,270 --> 00:34:39,920
Ju Eun Ho was very sick.

422
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:43,570
The fact that she disappeared so suddenly

423
00:34:44,620 --> 00:34:47,480
means she was in a lot of pain.

424
00:34:49,130 --> 00:34:50,930
Sunbaenim...

425
00:34:52,520 --> 00:34:55,090
don't you care about that at all?

426
00:34:56,610 --> 00:34:59,680
Do you not care that Ju Eun Ho was in pain?

427
00:35:00,550 --> 00:35:04,350
Do you only care that she dated me in that state?

428
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:08,740
I'm asking because I'm curious.

429
00:35:08,740 --> 00:35:10,890
Sunbaenim,

430
00:35:12,580 --> 00:35:14,930
what's important to you?

431
00:35:39,070 --> 00:35:40,510
Are you sick?

432
00:35:40,510 --> 00:35:42,320
Yeah. I'm sick.

433
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:44,330
Hyun Oh.

434
00:35:44,330 --> 00:35:45,790
Yeah? Tell me.

435
00:35:45,790 --> 00:35:48,900
I already have a doctor that I see.

436
00:35:57,500 --> 00:36:01,970
[Consent Form - Jung Hyun Oh]

437
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:06,770
Hello, Jung Hyun Oh?

438
00:36:08,560 --> 00:36:10,690
Oh, yes. Hello.

439
00:36:16,300 --> 00:36:20,960
Doctor, I'm a colleague of Ju Eun Ho.

440
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:23,910
Yes. How can I help you?

441
00:36:24,870 --> 00:36:27,320
I mean, I actually...

442
00:36:28,240 --> 00:36:31,260
used to be Eun Ho's boyfriend.

443
00:36:31,260 --> 00:36:35,020
I heard that she has Dissociative Identity Disorder.

444
00:36:35,020 --> 00:36:40,010
Did you come in to hear about Ju Eun Ho?

445
00:36:40,940 --> 00:36:44,520
Eun Ho is alone. She doesn't have a guardian. So I-

446
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:50,500
No. I'm sorry, but we do not provide information on our patients.

447
00:36:50,500 --> 00:36:54,680
I have an obligation to keep my conversations with patients confidential.

448
00:36:54,680 --> 00:36:57,380
- Eun Ho-
- Hyun Oh.

449
00:36:57,380 --> 00:37:03,000
As I've said, I cannot help you with that.

450
00:37:10,940 --> 00:37:17,450
But if you're okay with it, how about we talk about you?

451
00:37:36,510 --> 00:37:38,010
I...

452
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:41,190
Yes, tell me.

453
00:37:44,530 --> 00:37:46,540
I'm heartbroken.

454
00:37:47,350 --> 00:37:51,850
You mean your heart is in pain, right?

455
00:37:51,850 --> 00:37:54,420
Yes. My heart.

456
00:37:56,270 --> 00:38:00,250
Could you be more specific?

457
00:38:01,240 --> 00:38:03,010
So...

458
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:08,280
I had a girlfriend I broke up with four years ago.

459
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:09,950
She...

460
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:16,430
She has Dissociative Identity Disorder.

461
00:38:18,420 --> 00:38:20,480
But I heard about it

462
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:26,600
from a man whom she dated as her other personality.

463
00:38:28,170 --> 00:38:29,710
I know.

464
00:38:30,710 --> 00:38:33,830
I have no right.

465
00:38:33,830 --> 00:38:35,740
But Doctor.

466
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:39,930
Honestly, I didn't want to break up with her.

467
00:38:39,930 --> 00:38:43,670
You mean you didn't want to break up with your girlfriend.

468
00:38:43,670 --> 00:38:45,100
Correct.

469
00:38:45,100 --> 00:38:49,770
If I could, I wanted to be with her forever.

470
00:38:49,770 --> 00:38:52,210
But I had to break up with her.

471
00:38:52,210 --> 00:38:56,950
After that, she developed Dissociative Identity Disorder.

472
00:38:58,110 --> 00:39:00,590
She lived as a different person.

473
00:39:01,500 --> 00:39:03,710
And I had no idea.

474
00:39:05,410 --> 00:39:10,380
When you found out, how did you feel, Hyun Oh?

475
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:12,470
I was shocked.

476
00:39:14,430 --> 00:39:17,670
But what was equally shocking was the fact...

477
00:39:17,670 --> 00:39:21,500
that as her other personality, she was with another guy.

478
00:39:26,580 --> 00:39:28,340
I mean...

479
00:39:28,340 --> 00:39:31,770
how can I be only thinking of myself in this situation?

480
00:39:33,190 --> 00:39:36,880
Do you feel that you're selfish?

481
00:39:37,950 --> 00:39:41,870
I want to know why she's sick.

482
00:39:42,900 --> 00:39:44,980
Is it because of me?

483
00:39:45,890 --> 00:39:48,900
Is it my fault that she has this illness?

484
00:39:48,900 --> 00:39:50,370
Because...

485
00:39:51,130 --> 00:39:53,460
it feels too much like my fault.

486
00:39:54,540 --> 00:39:59,570
I see. It sounds like this has been very difficult for you.

487
00:39:59,570 --> 00:40:02,180
But Dissociative Identity Disorder

488
00:40:02,180 --> 00:40:07,410
might be widely known to be related to past trauma or stressful incidents,

489
00:40:07,410 --> 00:40:10,780
but many other factors affect it as well.

490
00:40:10,780 --> 00:40:15,680
So, we can't determine that it was your fault.

491
00:40:17,030 --> 00:40:19,810
Did I cause her to struggle and suffer?

492
00:40:19,810 --> 00:40:24,230
Is that why she's sick? Is this all because of me?

493
00:40:25,090 --> 00:40:26,820
Hyun Oh.

494
00:40:26,820 --> 00:40:31,800
I understand that you want to help Eun Ho.

495
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:35,810
But what we're talking about is related to Eun Ho.

496
00:40:35,810 --> 00:40:41,310
I need to talk about it with Eun Ho first and get her consent

497
00:40:41,310 --> 00:40:45,850
that she wants your help before I can help you.

498
00:40:47,120 --> 00:40:48,920
But...

499
00:40:48,920 --> 00:40:51,950
she doesn't tell me any of this.

500
00:40:54,860 --> 00:40:59,270
Hyun Oh, it seems like you're worried

501
00:40:59,270 --> 00:41:04,670
that breaking up with her may have really hurt Eun Ho.

502
00:41:06,810 --> 00:41:09,780
Yes. I am.

503
00:41:12,120 --> 00:41:17,080
I worry that it hurt her a lot.

504
00:41:18,340 --> 00:41:21,190
That she'll never get better.

505
00:41:21,190 --> 00:41:23,580
Doctor.

506
00:41:23,580 --> 00:41:26,940
How do you treat Dissociative Identity Disorder?

507
00:41:26,940 --> 00:41:30,930
Does she need to be hospitalized? Take medication?

508
00:41:31,740 --> 00:41:35,730
If necessary. But the most important thing

509
00:41:35,730 --> 00:41:40,150
is to talk it through and let the wounds heal.

510
00:41:41,110 --> 00:41:45,300
During the treatment process, when Eun Ho needs help,

511
00:41:45,300 --> 00:41:48,900
just knowing that someone is by her side

512
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:52,630
will be very comforting for her.

513
00:42:04,670 --> 00:42:06,800
Eun Ho.

514
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:10,100
Ju Eun Ho, are you inside?

515
00:42:13,160 --> 00:42:14,890
Ju Eun Ho!

516
00:42:17,770 --> 00:42:19,570
Eun Ho!

517
00:42:38,500 --> 00:42:44,890
[Kang Ju Yeon]

518
00:42:45,970 --> 00:42:49,180
[Missed calls from Kang Ju Yeon, Jung Hyun Oh]

519
00:43:01,510 --> 00:43:06,710
Me? Me? Me? I'm the best.

520
00:43:06,710 --> 00:43:11,150
I'm the best, best, best anchor. I am.

521
00:43:11,150 --> 00:43:13,930
Let's go, go, go.

522
00:43:13,930 --> 00:43:17,670
Hyun Oh. I came to ask you a question.

523
00:43:17,670 --> 00:43:19,810
Do you know where Ju Eun Ho went on vacation?

524
00:43:19,810 --> 00:43:21,490
Is she living somewhere else for a month?

525
00:43:21,490 --> 00:43:24,670
I want to try that kind of thing, too.

526
00:43:25,560 --> 00:43:27,260
I don't know, either.

527
00:43:28,060 --> 00:43:29,540
I see.

528
00:43:29,540 --> 00:43:32,010
Did her sister go with her, too?

529
00:43:32,010 --> 00:43:34,370
Her sister works at the parking lot I go to,

530
00:43:34,370 --> 00:43:38,170
but I haven't seen her in a while. If they left together...

531
00:43:38,170 --> 00:43:39,680
What?

532
00:43:40,410 --> 00:43:41,810
Huh?

533
00:43:41,810 --> 00:43:45,060
I park my car at the lot where Ju Eun Ho's sister works.

534
00:43:45,060 --> 00:43:51,490
Hey! I park there because that lot is weirdly flat!

